      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "歡迎收聽大人的Small Talk這是大人學的線上廣播節目我是Joe張國陽",
      "embedding": [],
      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:58:29.505576",
